  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK683">
<l>nūlārmu ṉūlvallā ṉākutal vēlārmuṉ </l>
<l>veṉṟi viṉaiyuraippāṉ paṇpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To be powerful in politics among those who are learned (in ethics) is the character of him who speaks to lance-bearing kings on matters of triumph (to his own sovereign).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
